          "1-cos(10°) ≈ 1-0.985 = 0.015",
          "v_max = √(2×10×2×0.015) = √0.6 ≈ 0.77 m/s"
        ],
        "answer": "T = 2.83 s ; v_max = 0.77 m/s",
        "formula_used": "T = 2π√(L/g)"
      },
